<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 01:27:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>特朗普的加密货币鼓舞人心的演讲无法阻止他的 Memecoin 的深度下滑</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-25/trump-s-crypto-pep-talk-can-t-stop-his-memecoin-s-deep-slide</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 再次承诺支持美国加密货币行业的增长，但未能重新点燃人们对他自己的模因币 (memecoin) 的兴趣，尽管总统向该代币的一些最大持有者发表讲话，但美元特朗普 (Trump) 周六仍下跌 14%。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/is1nygBkxosk/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 22:09:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-25/trump-s-crypto-pep-talk-can-t-stop-his-memecoin-s-deep-slide</guid></item><item><title>比特币悄然上涨，交易员将目光瞄准 80,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-25/bitcoin-s-stealth-rally-has-traders-setting-sights-on-80-000</link><description>比特币自 1 月份以来首次逼近 80,000 美元——这种隐形复苏不是建立在兴奋的基础上，而是建立在空头回补和一家公司的不懈积累之上：Strategy Inc. &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ieLWH7eWyjyo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 25 Apr 2026 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-25/bitcoin-s-stealth-rally-has-traders-setting-sights-on-80-000</guid></item><item><title>Crypto Faithful 以 500 美元赢得与特朗普的 Memecoin 午餐</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-24/crypto-faithful-wins-memecoin-lunch-with-trump-for-500</link><description>去年，莫滕·克里斯滕森 (Morten Christensen) 花费约 1,200 美元参加唐纳德·特朗普总统为总统模因币的顶级持有者举办的晚宴。今年，他将以 500 美元左右的价格参加类似的活动。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iGa41vNYEJFk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 16:01:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-24/crypto-faithful-wins-memecoin-lunch-with-trump-for-500</guid></item></channel></rss>